Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Documentation for LightOS
 Complete documentation for LightOS including:
  - Architecture guide
  - Modern features guide
  - Python API reference
  - Jupyter notebook tutorials
  - Deployment guides (Kubernetes, Docker, VM)
  .
  Includes example code and performance benchmarks.

Package: lightos-cuda
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: lightos (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         nvidia-driver (>= 525),
         nvidia-cuda-toolkit (>= 12.0)
Description: NVIDIA CUDA support for LightOS
 CUDA-accelerated kernels for LightOS inference on NVIDIA GPUs.
 .
 Provides optimized kernels for:
  - Matrix multiplication (cuBLAS, Tensor Cores)
  - Convolutions (cuDNN)
  - Attention mechanisms (Flash Attention)
  - Sparse operations (cuSPARSE)

Package: lightos-rocm
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: lightos (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         rocm-core (>= 5.0)
Description: AMD ROCm support for LightOS
 ROCm-accelerated kernels for LightOS inference on AMD GPUs (MI200, MI300).
 .
 Provides optimized kernels for:
  - Matrix multiplication (rocBLAS)
  - Convolutions (MIOpen)
  - Sparse operations (rocSPARSE)
